    "translatedContent": "| `/recall-context` | Claude가 현재 로드한 메모리를 보여줌 |"
  },
  {
    "row": 93,
    "rowsha": "0Mylrl51OWT51T3vOGM1Qw5n4LuEdWSVV/CHwcDtRuI=",
    "originContent": "| `/recall-context` | Show what memory Claude has loaded right now |",
    "translatedContent": ""
  },
  {
    "row": 94,
    "rowsha": "47DEQpj8HBSa+/TImW+5JCeuQeRkm5NMpJWZG3hSuFU=",
    "originContent": "",
    "translatedContent": "플러그인으로 설치된 경우, 명령어는 네임스페이스가 붙습니다: `/recall:recall-write` 대신 `/recall-write`."
  },
  {
    "row": 95,
    "rowsha": "wR5CJS/P4Y8slnpDXwcs16XHZ+NEYK4G3W6o8xfJwXQ=",
    "originContent": "If installed as a plugin, commands are namespaced: `/recall:recall-write` instead of `/recall-write`.",
    "translatedContent": ""
  },
  {
    "row": 96,
    "rowsha": "47DEQpj8HBSa+/TImW+5JCeuQeRkm5NMpJWZG3hSuFU=",
    "originContent": "",
    "translatedContent": "## 작성 게이트"
  },
  {
    "row": 97,
    "rowsha": "nbzJ5Fek+lqGVHPv08Ff1Wh7A8KQ8vYkfUjGSaXJnpY=",
    "originContent": "## The Write Gate",
    "translatedContent": ""
  },
  {
    "row": 98,
    "rowsha": "47DEQpj8HBSa+/TImW+5JCeuQeRkm5NMpJWZG3hSuFU=",
    "originContent": "",
    "translatedContent": "이것이 핵심 아이디어입니다. 영구 메모리로 승격되기 전에, 적어도 하나 이상의 검사를 통과해야 합니다:"
  },
  {
    "row": 99,
    "rowsha": "PWSYd7W4sNbE/NxaD/rmm2YKhv5sUStGOa4p09PFW7E=",
    "originContent": "This is the core idea. Before anything gets promoted to permanent memory, it has to pass at least one of these checks:",
    "translatedContent": ""
  },
  {
    "row": 100,
    "rowsha": "47DEQpj8HBSa+/TImW+5JCeuQeRkm5NMpJWZG3hSuFU=",
    "originContent": "",
    "translatedContent": "1. **다음에 Claude의 행동 방식을 바꿀 것인가?** (선호, 경계, 패턴)"
  },
  {
    "row": 101,
    "rowsha": "XfUrX+NJ6ME153a2xmsg91EzTsybBFAIrpaPqO6xwkg=",
    "originContent": "1. **Will it change how Claude behaves next time?** (a preference, a boundary, a pattern)",
    "translatedContent": "2. **누군가가 기대하는 약속인가?** (마감일, 결과물, 후속 조치)"
  },
  {
    "row": 102,
    "rowsha": "iCApm+2W1X8McMHI3/VB8z2QFnfd4JegoMV/CezkeL0=",
    "originContent": "2. **Is it a commitment someone's counting on?** (a deadline, a deliverable, a follow-up)",
    "translatedContent": "3. **이유를 기억할 가치가 있는 결정인가?** (X를 선택한 이유)"
  },
  {
    "row": 103,
    "rowsha": "CxphoEjOJS9fKvVt0U7PkuzkLWjBRq8FLQWDyTWtjPg=",
    "originContent": "3. **Is it a decision worth remembering the reasoning for?** (why you picked X over Y)",
    "translatedContent": "4. **다시 등장할 안정적인 사실인가?** (내일 달라지지 않을 정보)"
  },
  {
    "row": 104,
    "rowsha": "d62twwZlsA2O+N2AR7T38W6EkjLdWbOZXjx0A1JxXNY=",
    "originContent": "4. **Is it a stable fact that'll come up again?** (not something that'll be different tomorrow)",
    "translatedContent": "5. **명시적으로 \"기억해둬\"라고 말했는가?**"
  },
  {
    "row": 105,
    "rowsha": "O1K03SkZlyyw3nXeVJCJaWJWgM7RRex+ayFRHwQZoHE=",
    "originContent": "5. **Did you explicitly say \"remember this\"?**",
    "translatedContent": ""
  },
  {
    "row": 106,
    "rowsha": "47DEQpj8HBSa+/TImW+5JCeuQeRkm5NMpJWZG3hSuFU=",
    "originContent": "",
    "translatedContent": "이 중 어느 것도 해당하지 않으면 일일 노트에 남아 결국 사라집니다. 메모리를 간결하게 유지합니다. 잡동사니 서랍 없음."
  },
  {
    "row": 107,
    "rowsha": "Z+IortAcHG0xYRswjyQkqxRlDuXle+sQ8uhE8mhiC7w=",
    "originContent": "If none of those are true, it stays in the daily notebook and eventually ages out. This keeps memory lean. No junk drawer.",
    "translatedContent": ""
  },
  {
    "row": 108,
    "rowsha": "47DEQpj8HBSa+/TImW+5JCeuQeRkm5NMpJWZG3hSuFU=",
    "originContent": "",
    "translatedContent": "## 수정이 발생할 때"
  },
  {
    "row": 109,
    "rowsha": "mF6Dx1gWiJiW+jhs8BTaYhbPHw3MNEHdsmjVyMfe/bA=",
    "originContent": "## When Corrections Happen",
    "translatedContent": ""
  },
  {
    "row": 110,
    "rowsha": "47DEQpj8HBSa+/TImW+5JCeuQeRkm5NMpJWZG3hSuFU=",
    "originContent": "",
    "translatedContent": "Claude가 잘못된 정보를 받았다고 하면, 단순히 \"죄송합니다\"라고 하고 넘어가지 않습니다. 일일 노트, 관련 레지스터, 카운터를 한 번에 업데이트합니다. 이전 정보는 대체됨으로 표시되며(삭제되지 않음), 무엇이 언제 변경되었는지 기록으로 남습니다."
  },
  {
    "row": 111,
    "rowsha": "mEw1dcAOaQMsSepbaqBzzhsJqbIfKIp26OC9QqucA3E=",
    "originContent": "If you tell Claude it got something wrong, it doesn't just say \"sorry\" and move on. It updates the daily notebook, the relevant register, and the counter, all in one shot. The old information gets marked as superseded (not deleted) so there's a trail of what changed and when.",
    "translatedContent": ""
  },
  {
    "row": 112,
    "rowsha": "47DEQpj8HBSa+/TImW+5JCeuQeRkm5NMpJWZG3hSuFU=",
    "originContent": "",
    "translatedContent": "## 자동으로 로드되는 것"
  },
  {
    "row": 113,
    "rowsha": "SRRPf6YIchuC3ICjxgB/qPvsDLfLvarbDI/+dS/2xLI=",
    "originContent": "## What Loads Automatically",
    "translatedContent": ""
  },
  {
    "row": 114,
    "rowsha": "47DEQpj8HBSa+/TImW+5JCeuQeRkm5NMpJWZG3hSuFU=",
    "originContent": "",
    "translatedContent": "매 세션마다 두 가지만 로드됩니다:"
  },
  {
    "row": 115,
    "rowsha": "VCS5tfF7v3EhfZ6fu539+KBfwsPmqUB9Kx23fDKtBFI=",
    "originContent": "Only two things, every session:",
    "translatedContent": ""
  },
  {
    "row": 116,
    "rowsha": "47DEQpj8HBSa+/TImW+5JCeuQeRkm5NMpJWZG3hSuFU=",
    "originContent": "",
    "translatedContent": "| 항목 | 위치 | 방법 |"
  },
  {
    "row": 117,
    "rowsha": "9ciud8XnvJ5t6g3RSg1U4n4n1AKqteq9KUhb7ERAy40=",
    "originContent": "| What | Where | How |",
    "translatedContent": ""
  },
  {
    "row": 118,
    "rowsha": "I8ygK3TzhkY++iR5bHqQEbDSyT8MOLTRXV0nYgW1m0M=",
    "originContent": "|---|---|---|",
    "translatedContent": "|---|---|---|"
  },
  {
    "row": 119,
    "rowsha": "JSPUL4EnRToUc7h+WQ5bzX9gBy1M8HpwAS+YYSnItcs=",
    "originContent": "| The rules (write gate, correction protocol) | `rules/total-recall.md` | Claude Code loads all rules files automatically |",
    "translatedContent": "| 규칙들 (작성 게이트, 수정 프로토콜) | `rules/total-recall.md` | Claude Code는 모든 규칙 파일을 자동으로 로드합니다 |"
  },
  {
    "row": 120,
    "rowsha": "Dg6Rk8astaAPHG2Uc2xyhHm8erifNu5ycuaesKWqg4M=",
    "originContent": "| Counter / working memory | `CLAUDE.local.md` | Claude Code loads this automatically |",
    "translatedContent": "| 카운터 / 작업 메모리 | `CLAUDE.local.md` | Claude Code가 이를 자동으로 로드합니다 |"
  },
  {
    "row": 121,
    "rowsha": "47DEQpj8HBSa+/TImW+5JCeuQeRkm5NMpJWZG3hSuFU=",
    "originContent": "",
    "translatedContent": ""
  },
  {
    "row": 122,
    "rowsha": "aEVc4HRAUPZ6xc6VJg/cCqJtfMuPtE37u4z4Kp6joXk=",
    "originContent": "Everything else loads on demand: when you search, when it's relevant, or at session start via hooks.",
    "translatedContent": "나머지는 필요에 따라 로드됩니다: 검색할 때, 관련 있을 때, 또는 세션 시작 시 훅을 통해서."
  },
  {
    "row": 123,
    "rowsha": "47DEQpj8HBSa+/TImW+5JCeuQeRkm5NMpJWZG3hSuFU=",
    "originContent": "",
    "translatedContent": ""
  },
  {
    "row": 124,
    "rowsha": "bfv6uMqO/8TGua3ajeL5s7AKeb9WgtbbUmgxo83mS+M=",
    "originContent": "## Hooks",
    "translatedContent": "## 훅"
  },
  {
    "row": 125,
    "rowsha": "47DEQpj8HBSa+/TImW+5JCeuQeRkm5NMpJWZG3hSuFU=",
    "originContent": "",
    "translatedContent": ""
  },
  {
    "row": 126,
    "rowsha": "jUBHct4io1t3f8DX836DXFPumvgFVv/t9+4Ku5+bc3E=",
    "originContent": "Two things happen automatically in the background:",
    "translatedContent": "두 가지 작업이 백그라운드에서 자동으로 일어납니다:"
  },
  {
    "row": 127,
    "rowsha": "47DEQpj8HBSa+/TImW+5JCeuQeRkm5NMpJWZG3hSuFU=",
    "originContent": "",
    "translatedContent": ""
  },
  {
    "row": 128,
    "rowsha": "sX1EZJiR5DGoxDTt4XzaG0fx5h6Y35R5+0l6mqXGwXQ=",
    "originContent": "**When a session starts:** Claude gets a summary of open items and recent daily notes. This is the \"here's where we left off\" briefing.",
    "translatedContent": "**세션이 시작될 때:** Claude는 미처리 항목과 최근 일일 노트의 요약을 받습니다. 이것이 \"우리가 어디까지 했는지\" 브리핑입니다."
  },
  {
    "row": 129,
    "rowsha": "47DEQpj8HBSa+/TImW+5JCeuQeRkm5NMpJWZG3hSuFU=",
    "originContent": "",
    "translatedContent": ""
  },
  {
    "row": 130,
    "rowsha": "4u1O+Em3SpqJ3mru0oVl1xz3P30/TXRbm+P1oGJwDNY=",
    "originContent": "**Before memory gets compacted:** A timestamp gets written to the daily notebook so there's a record. This one is silent. Claude doesn't see it, it's just bookkeeping.",
    "translatedContent": "**메모리가 압축되기 전에:** 타임스탬프가 일일 노트북에 기록되어 기록이 남습니다. 이 작업은 조용히 진행됩니다. Claude는 이것을 보지 못하며, 단지 회계용입니다."
  },
  {
    "row": 131,
    "rowsha": "47DEQpj8HBSa+/TImW+5JCeuQeRkm5NMpJWZG3hSuFU=",
    "originContent": "",
    "translatedContent": ""
  },
  {
    "row": 132,
    "rowsha": "hSeqKwqr8ygQIUMt8SORlFU1S6QYPMNgaQf0zkJMF/w=",
    "originContent": "Both hooks fail safely. If something goes wrong, they don't block Claude Code from working.",
    "translatedContent": "두 훅 모두 안전하게 실패합니다. 문제가 발생해도 Claude Code 작동을 막지 않습니다."
  },
  {
    "row": 133,
    "rowsha": "47DEQpj8HBSa+/TImW+5JCeuQeRkm5NMpJWZG3hSuFU=",
    "originContent": "",
    "translatedContent": ""
  },
  {
    "row": 134,
    "rowsha": "1Fg5i8HpkF+UU9RF5HiJ/fTd4Zo8RNO2eFKdS0LN2Y8=",
    "originContent": "Hooks use `$CLAUDE_PROJECT_DIR` (standalone) or `${CLAUDE_PLUGIN_ROOT}` (plugin) to resolve paths. No transcript parsing. The PreCompact hook only writes a timestamp marker to the daily log. It does not read or parse conversation transcripts.",
    "translatedContent": "훅은 경로를 해결하기 위해 `$CLAUDE_PROJECT_DIR` (독립형) 또는 `${CLAUDE_PLUGIN_ROOT}` (플러그인)를 사용합니다. 대화 기록을 파싱하지 않습니다. PreCompact 훅은 단지 일일 로그에 타임스탬프 마커만 씁니다. 대화 기록을 읽거나 파싱하지 않습니다."
  },
  {
    "row": 135,
    "rowsha": "47DEQpj8HBSa+/TImW+5JCeuQeRkm5NMpJWZG3hSuFU=",
    "originContent": "",
    "translatedContent": ""
  },
  {
    "row": 136,
    "rowsha": "p+VkcrEb08g4vIGZYB9aVScRKgA8afv5WwErwTVzoZM=",
    "originContent": "## Architecture",
    "translatedContent": "## 아키텍처"
  },
  {
    "row": 137,
    "rowsha": "47DEQpj8HBSa+/TImW+5JCeuQeRkm5NMpJWZG3hSuFU=",
    "originContent": "",
    "translatedContent": ""
  },
  {
    "row": 138,
    "rowsha": "qJIUOcMJZ24kkGr1K73pghfe1X3UC6jAV47FqinsAto=",
    "originContent": "For those who want the technical details.",
    "translatedContent": "기술적인 세부사항을 원하는 분들을 위해."
  },
  {
    "row": 139,
    "rowsha": "47DEQpj8HBSa+/TImW+5JCeuQeRkm5NMpJWZG3hSuFU=",
    "originContent": "",
    "translatedContent": ""
  },
  {
    "row": 140,
    "rowsha": "8bkBhHOQsO1+N058HkZOwXtGpCfEh6WtbL0pBkBQg9U=",
    "originContent": "```",
    "translatedContent": "```"
  },
  {
    "row": 141,
    "rowsha": "D+Wnao3QJMTKmyvyqbQEKCHpHGRE8YIiLPYjk1wRJMg=",
    "originContent": "Conversation (ephemeral, compacted/discarded)",
    "translatedContent": "Conversation (ephemeral, compacted/discarded)"
  },
  {
    "row": 142,
    "rowsha": "ahMlSl1RG4uLFyGzW1Zd8Kq3WGZzf0vbJJoXb61yQe0=",
